functions.name: main
body: let products: list<Product> = [Product(name: "Laptop", price: 1500), Product(name: "Smartphone", price: 900), Product(name: "Tablet", price: 600), Product(name: "Monitor", price: 300), Product(name: "Keyboard", price: 100), Product(name: "Mouse", price: 50), Product(name: "Headphones", price: 200)]
let expensive = (List.of([for (var p in products) p])..sort(((a, b) => b.price.compareTo(a.price)))).skip(1).take(3).toList()
